description:
Remember when the media went after and condemned the Biden administration’s withdrawal from Afghanistan after Americans died? Me neither. That is why JD Vance called out the media for obsessing over the Signal story but turning a blind eye to the Afghanistan withdrawal.

🔥BOOM: JD Vance just TORCHED the legacy media for calling for resignations after running cover for the DISASTROUS Biden administration’s withdrawal from Afghanistan. pic.twitter.com/aFzePiwgdx
— Townhall.com (@townhallcom) March 28, 2025

It's not possible to sum it up
title: JD Vance GOES THERE, torches media over SignalGate after they shilled for Joe Biden's disastrous Afghanistan withdrawal

description:
More than half the country has no trouble answering the question: "What is a woman?" However, there is a fringe minority who struggle with this concept that even cavemen understood. This is why Trump had to inform these gender confused individuals what an adult female is.

WATCH @POTUS answer a journalist who asked him, "What is a woman?":

"It's sort of easy to answer for me because a woman is somebody that can have a baby under certain circumstances. A woman is a person who is much smarter than a man, I've always found." 🤣 pic.twitter.com/HEGwwQrIJj
— Trump War Room (@TrumpWarRoom)
title: Donald Trump gets grilled by reporter if he knows "what is a woman," gives EPIC response

description:
It’s time to make fat shaming great again.

RFK Jr. publicly told West Virginia Gov. Patrick Morrisey that he needs to lose 30 pounds and called for monthly weigh-ins during a state press conference to ban food dyes in school lunches.

NEW: RFK Jr. tells West Virginia Gov. Patrick Morrisey that he needs to lose 30 pounds to his face, calls on Morrisey to do a "public weigh-in" every month.

The Health Secretary is now fat-shaming people in public. Amazing.

"I said, 'You look like you ate Governor Morrissey.'"… pic.twitter.com/knJwos0paR
— Collin Rugg (@CollinRugg) March 28, 2025
title: RFK Jr. is fat-shaming governors to their faces, and it's amazing
